I just posted a hello to Anne, and then realized it may have been at
unschooling.com list she posted to!! Sheesh.
AOL tried to merge my CS account and screwed my account up so that I
can't reply to any digests via my regular address. They are fixing
it, but in the meantime I have to actually log on to the list to post
anything!!
So forgive me if I accidentally post to the wrong list.
Was Anne here or am I totally mixed up?
Argh...
Ren
